WEBVTT

00:07:31.173 --> 00:07:32.944
requesting an interview,

00:07:32.968 --> 00:07:35.346
and I sent it to his Tower in New York.

00:07:35.370 --> 00:07:36.600
The next day

00:07:37.285 --> 00:07:38.484
I was at work,

00:07:38.508 --> 00:07:42.081
and I suddenly began to receive
hundreds of calls and texts

00:07:42.105 --> 00:07:43.594
on my cell phone,

00:07:43.618 --> 00:07:45.160
some more insulting than others.

00:07:45.184 --> 00:07:48.681
I didn't know what was happening
until my friend came into my office

00:07:48.705 --> 00:07:52.473
and said, "They published
your cell number online."

00:07:53.608 --> 00:07:55.053
They actually did that.

00:07:55.944 --> 00:07:59.318
Here's the letter they sent

00:07:59.342 --> 00:08:01.560
where they gave out my number.